HEADWORD: Delightful
<hw>De*light"ful</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Highly pleasing;
affording great pleasure and satisfaction.</def>
⟦ldquo⟧<xex>Delightful</xex> bowers.⟦rdquo⟧ <au>Spenser.</au>
⟦ldquo⟧<xex>Delightful</xex> fruit.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Milton.</au></rj></p>

<p><syn><b>Syn.</b> -- Delicious; charming. See
<er>Delicious</er>.</syn></p>

<p>-- <wordforms><wf>De*light"ful*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos> --
<wf>De*light"ful*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
